                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17881022-2-off7 t17881022-2-crimeloc10"></join> about ten o'clock to the Sessions-house, the prisoner picked my pocket; I did not know it till Newman came up to me and said, Mr. Akerman, here is a man has picked your pocket; Newman pulled up the man's apron and the handkerchief was taken out of his breeches.</p>
               <p>NEWMAN sworn.</p>
               <p>I saw the prisoner take it, and I informed Mr. Akerman, and I took the handkerchief out of the prisoner's breeches in Mr. Akerman's presence.</p>
